[[#comment]]


** 例

[8] 連結によって実現値化する例
[PRE(HTML)[
<P><OBJECT declare
        id="EARTH.DECLARATION" 
        data="TheEarth.mpeg" 
        type="video/mpeg">
   The <STRONG>Earth</STRONG> as seen from space.
</OBJECT>
...later in the document...
